{"tid":2376380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白羅斯因疫情及政局動盪 遭IIHF褫奪世界冰上曲棍球錦標賽舉辦資格","createTime":"2021-01-22T17:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T12:15:52.000Z","uid":18692,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a1759e1ad165ef2d83afbe8c9ddbc31d9c948096","tid":2376380,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T17:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xbMsLQX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxbMsLQX.jpg&h=4c47ae3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際冰上曲棍球總會（IIHF）因應疫情及政局動盪，褫奪白羅斯今屆世界冰上曲棍球錦標賽的舉辦資格，賽事有加拿大、俄羅斯及瑞典等強國參加。<br />\n<br />\n今屆原定5月至6月由白羅斯和拉脫維亞合辦，前者負責A組、4強及決賽。白羅斯過去數月染疫人口不斷激增。去年8月大選充滿爭議，連串示威遭政府鎮壓，至今超過3萬人被捕、50人失蹤。此舉在國際形象相當負面，國內外一直施壓取消其主辦權。<br />\n<br />\n1月中旬IIHF主席前往白羅斯，會面總統盧卡申科。總統不但沒有保持社交距離，甚至連口罩都不戴就擁抱他。 <br />\n<br />\n會上盧卡申科輕描淡寫地說明國家在政治和疫情各方面都無問題。他以熱愛冰上曲棍球聞名，於疫情肆虐期間仍落場比賽。<br />\n<br />\n捷克汽車品牌Skoda及德國機油大廠Liqui Moly日前表示，如世錦賽繼續於白羅斯首都明斯克舉行，將以人權理由取消贊助。<br />\n<br />\n2018年冬奧滑雪金牌得主侯絲高娃（Hanna Huskova） 等400名職業運動員，去年聯署公開信不承認大選結果，並要求釋放政治犯。08年奧運田徑十項全能銀牌Andrei Krautshanka因參與示威被監禁10日，其後被踢出國家隊。<br />\n<br />\n因此國際奧委會（IOC）今週公布，禁止盧卡申科及其子參與奧運活動，例如東京奧運會觀賽，資助亦會繞過該國奧委會，直接發放予運動員。 <br />\n<br />\n而IIHF經過評估後，認為在白羅斯舉辦賽事，所有參賽隊伍、觀眾和各國官方人士的安全不受保障，決定取消該國的共同主辦權。<br />\n<br />\n身處立陶宛的抗爭象徵季哈諾夫斯卡婭對決定表示歡迎。俄羅斯社會政策委員會副主席表示，剝奪賽事舉辦權為政治決定，白羅斯可尋求賠償。  <br />\n<br />\n拉脫維亞政府早前計劃杯葛與白羅斯合辦，將評估如何順利舉辦這屆比賽。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=884556\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D884556&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=67c380c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D884556&h=8ab9fc49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=884556</a>"},{"pid":"12c7f6c435501aa6caf83b5c6054f533a350e98b","tid":2376380,"uid":389613,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T17:54:04.000Z","msg":"BAN 北京冬奧啦，committed genocide against Uighurs 呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389348d324bb1fba29d377eac4d0c9248065e2b4","tid":2376380,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T19:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae4efe62dd007a6207bfe4cbf144e67ab9dcf39","tid":2376380,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T19:04:24.000Z","msg":"左膠：相信制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f522af89d7409a5509b7c839a6e027f0a059a665","tid":2376380,"uid":33028,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T20:08:48.000Z","msg":"係白俄羅斯"},{"pid":"c7c9f7847ccb4e750354cb06b7b73b20c41cc308","tid":2376380,"uid":119844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T21:54:55.000Z","msg":"武肺開始大爆個期仲曾經係世一足球聯賽"},{"pid":"e09b48fe15d78c79efc1a885b13c088ec8c4fcb4","tid":2376380,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T22:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd24bf4f83670721cabb1fc7d502dec4bfd3fe16","tid":2376380,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T22:28:28.000Z","msg":"白羅斯"},{"pid":"f2b280dd1d7a3453b75e48912f82342876be40a2","tid":2376380,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T22:48:24.000Z","msg":"請ioc禁埋林奠習近平有份逼害香港人、新疆人、蒙古族<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6caadac7110b3c48ed7970026381cea5946ebbbf","tid":2376380,"uid":136299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T23:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa70f7e9ca4eed79eef3e5db266c88871f5403bf","tid":2376380,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T23:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af65f3850af80c67284a2611e895b43ef6d7dbe","tid":2376380,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T08:37:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/WorldPentathlon/status/1352619399853858820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWorldPentathlon%2Fstatus%2F1352619399853858820&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=a6af2d54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWorldPentathlon%2Fstatus%2F1352619399853858820&h=7b225782\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/WorldPentathlon/status/1352619399853858820</a><br />\n噤日國際現代五項總會<br />\n都取消今年白羅斯世錦賽主辦權"},{"pid":"f062a0be5d98a15d67e191a12b5eee518bcdbab5","tid":2376380,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f90cbe62910c50a0df733e7c473578e4170503","tid":2376380,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uTM8CWn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuTM8CWn.jpg&h=68fb0ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0yiZ9H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0yiZ9H.jpg&h=cad7e5f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68dd3bb6b63aea8e4d890c1a30d19c049394cafe","tid":2376380,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b32bead3622d1917a7301291923a87ba353fb27","tid":2376380,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f522af89d7409a5509b7c839a6e027f0a059a665","tid":2376380,"uid":33028,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T20:08:48.000Z","msg":"係白俄羅斯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"白國駐北京大使館16日發佈聲明稱，「白俄羅斯」的說法是錯誤的，國家並不是俄羅斯的一部分，今後希望把中文國名正名為「白羅斯」，這樣不會跟俄羅斯混為一談。<br />\n<br />\n「白俄羅斯」可能會誤解為白色的俄羅斯人，但並不正確。白國聲明指出，如果要從語言和語意的角度來翻譯他們的國名，應該用「白羅斯」一詞。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20180317/ZVEKEK2XT46IX34HMYTLHG2GYA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20180317%2FZVEKEK2XT46IX34HMYTLHG2GYA%2F&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=dbd815a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20180317%2FZVEKEK2XT46IX34HMYTLHG2GYA%2F&h=c5977a58\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20180317/ZVEKEK2XT46IX34HMYTLHG2GYA/</a>"},{"pid":"465ffa58aecdc0252cd58b1e4a23caf938be9980","tid":2376380,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b32bead3622d1917a7301291923a87ba353fb27","tid":2376380,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f522af89d7409a5509b7c839a6e027f0a059a665","tid":2376380,"uid":33028,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T20:08:48.000Z","msg":"係白俄羅斯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"白國駐北京大使館16日發佈聲明稱，「白俄羅斯」的說法是錯誤的，國家並不是俄羅斯的一部分，今後希望把中文國名正名為「白羅斯」，這樣不會跟俄羅斯混為一談。<br />\n<br />\n「白俄羅斯」可能會誤解為白色的俄羅斯人，但並不正確。白國聲明指出，如果要從語言和語意的角度來翻譯他們的國名，應該用「白羅斯」一詞。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20180317/ZVEKEK2XT46IX34HMYTLHG2GYA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20180317%2FZVEKEK2XT46IX34HMYTLHG2GYA%2F&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=dbd815a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20180317%2FZVEKEK2XT46IX34HMYTLHG2GYA%2F&h=c5977a58\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20180317/ZVEKEK2XT46IX34HMYTLHG2GYA/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"呢個係個獨裁政權單方面改名。"},{"pid":"817e631163ad338b31a402a503f047811eace877","tid":2376380,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"拉脫維亞人口有190萬<br />\n國土都喺世錦賽最細<br />\nIIHF而家考慮幾個方案<br />\n1) 拉脫維亞包辦全部比賽<br />\n2) 白羅斯部分由丹麥舉辦<br />\n3) 部分轉俾斯洛伐克"},{"pid":"4c951ed1b6159f5e1bfe865c09f067bca34d55b8","tid":2376380,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:15:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PJ9wbvGd3I4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPJ9wbvGd3I4&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=186ca0e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PJ9wbvGd3I4</a><br />\n段片有上年兩個香港攝記<br />\n去咗當地影示威嘅經歷"}]}